reviewText: I was a huge fan of Kenny vs Spenny. This is pretty much like the Kenny side without the competition. A lot of the episodes kind of meander around without a real purpose. Good for a one time watch through, but no staying power. Also, a couple of the episodes become un-watchable because they are so awkward or gross. If you're a Kenny Hotz fan, I would recommend.
Kenny hotz is the man! Great show hope to see more soon.
